item.title: Allowed Metric Names
item.description: Name Description SyncookiesSent An application wasn’t able to accept a connection fast enough, so the kernel couldn’t store an entry in the queue for this connection. Instead of dropping it, it sent a cookie to the client. SyncookiesRecv After sending a cookie, it came back to us and passed the check. SyncookiesFailed After sending a cookie, it came back to us but looked invalid.
